Package: RDSensDisc
Type: Package
Title: Test for continuity in regression discontinuity
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Dor Leventer
Maintainer: <dorleventer@mail.tau.ac.il>
Description: Given an regression discontinuity treatment effect estimator and observed data, the package provides functions for calculating what is the highest treatment effect that would not reject the null hypothesis and tests whether the original treatment effect estimator is equal to it. 
